title: My 12 Scans (gnv64)
description:
On the occasion of the  KickAss Upload Day 2015, I am uploading this torrent containing 12 books scanned by me over past few weeks. All are in PDF format with OCR, bookmarks & covers. Covers included in separate folder:

01. ABC of Popular Misconceptions by Uday Lal
02. Children Who Made It Big by Thangamani
03. Decalog 4 - Regenerations by Andy Lane & Justin Richards (Ed)
04. Decalog 5 - Wonders by Paul Leonard & Jim Mortimore (Ed)
05. Doing Simple Math in Your Head by W.J.Howard
06. How to Lie With Statistics by Darrell Huff
07. Jungle Lore by Jim Corbett
08. Labyrinth by litizen.com
09. Letters from a Father to his Daughter by Jawaharlal Nehru
10. My Best Mathematical and Logic Puzzles by Martin Gardner
11. Pyramid for Health & Happiness by A.R.Hari
12. World's Best Mystery & Defective Stories (Various)
